src="https://gam0022.net/blog/2024/01/01/ue5-pcg-introduction-tips/example02-result-after_hu_9bc54aa951aa79b6.webp"
width="760"
height="428"
loading="lazy" data-zoomable /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;これがPCG Graphです。オレンジ色の枠で部分がExample01から新しく追加した処理です。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
&lt;figure &gt;
&lt;div class="flex justify-center "&gt;
&lt;div class="w-full" &gt;
&lt;img alt="Example02: Graphの全体"
srcset="https://gam0022.net/blog/2024/01/01/ue5-pcg-introduction-tips/example02-graph1_hu_3b63712af970309e.webp 320w, https://gam0022.net/blog/2024/01/01/ue5-pcg-introduction-tips/example02-graph1_hu_9d1f4bcb5cfb304b.webp 480w, https://gam0022.net/blog/2024/01/01/ue5-pcg-introduction-tips/example02-graph1_hu_5f830930b09e746a.webp 760w"
sizes="(max-width: 480px) 100vw, (max-width: 768px) 90vw, (max-width: 1024px) 80vw, 760px"
